---
import RegionSection from "./RegionSection.astro";
---

<RegionSection
    title="Geography"
    subtitle="The landscape of the Golden Heartland."
>

<div class="feature">

    <p>

        Endless golden plains and gently rolling hills define much of Solmara's
        landscape. Fertile farmland stretches across the region before giving
        way to towering southern cliffs overlooking the Great Lake. Along the
        eastern coastline, the Solaris Mountain Range protects the region from
        the powerful ocean winds.

    </p>

</div>

</RegionSection>

<style>

.feature{

    max-width:900px;

    margin:auto;

    text-align:center;

}

.feature p{

    color:var(--muted);

    line-height:2;

    font-size:1.1rem;

}

</style>